If there's one thing we can all be sure of it's that Mzansi is always ready to turn lemons into sweet lemonade when it comes to our never-ending political problems. So when former Bosasa COO Angelo Agrizzi  kicked off 2019 with shocking testimony during the state capture commission of inquiry, it was only a matter of time before South Africans dealt with their disbelief through humour. Here are some of the best memes to be shared on social media during Agrizzi’s nearly two week testimony: